title: 'Not sturdy and 3 of 4 sockets stopped working in one month'
body: 'Design is good and convenient. Plug points became loose within a month of use. Wasted money.'

title: 'Medium Quantity'
column5: One switch out of three is not working from the first day.'

title: 'No earthing socket'
body: I don't understand why there is no earthing socket.
